xmcr (0.3.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added archive support: the list of comics is kept offline for improved
    navigation
  * Added favorites support: favorites are kept offline
  * Added share support using the system accounts
  * Added swipe support to move around in the Comic View
  * Added l10n support and Spanish, English, German, French and Portuguese
    translations
  * Added a progress bar to display loading progress for images

 -- Simon Pena <spena@igalia.com>  Sat, 29 Oct 2011 20:50:22 +0300

